{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/srcsim/pullrequests/19/comments/28673361.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/srcsim/pull-requests/19/_/diff#comment-28673361"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 19, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/srcsim/pullrequests/19.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/srcsim/pull-requests/19"}}, "title": "Scoring"}, "content": {"raw": "It was brought to my attention that there is an offset between the head frame and `upperNeckPitchLink`. I'll update the script to take that into account. I believe the offset is:\n~~~\n  <joint name=\"multisense_head_root_joint\" type=\"fixed\">\n    <origin rpy=\"-3.14159 0.130899694 0.0\" xyz=\"0.183585961 0.0 0.075353826\"/>\n    <axis xyz=\"0 0 1\"/>\n    <parent link=\"upperNeckPitchLink\"/>\n    <child link=\"head\"/>\n  </joint>\n~~~\n", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>It was brought to my attention that there is an offset between the head frame and <code>upperNeckPitchLink</code>. I'll update the script to take that into account. I believe the offset is:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;joint</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;multisense_head_root_joint&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">type=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;fixed&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;origin</span> <span class=\"na\">rpy=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;-3.14159 0.130899694 0.0&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">xyz=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0.183585961 0.0 0.075353826&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;axis</span> <span class=\"na\">xyz=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0 0 1&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;parent</span> <span class=\"na\">link=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;upperNeckPitchLink&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;child</span> <span class=\